<paragraph blockId="30.[151,1436,938,1964]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,275,1858,1884]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Notes.</emphasis>
Basal portion of elytra orange, elytral spots yellow. Similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta, 2010" authorityName="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta" authorityYear="2010" box="[1011,1262,1859,1884]" class="Insecta" family="Scirtidae" genus="Scirtes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="philippinensis" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[1011,1262,1859,1884]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Scirtes philippinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1269,1334,1858,1884]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, but elytral suture orange (black in 
<taxonomicName authority="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta, 2010" authorityName="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta" authorityYear="2010" box="[477,671,1898,1924]" class="Insecta" family="Scirtidae" genus="Scirtes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="philippinensis" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[477,492,1899,1924]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[507,671,1899,1924]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">philippinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[680,744,1898,1924]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
), penis as long as parameres (much longer than parameres in 
<taxonomicName authority="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta, 2010" authorityName="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta" authorityYear="2010" box="[181,374,1938,1964]" class="Insecta" family="Scirtidae" genus="Scirtes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="philippinensis" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[181,196,1939,1964]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[210,374,1939,1964]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">philippinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[382,447,1938,1964]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
). Aedeagus similar to the one of 
<taxonomicName authority="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta, 2010" authorityName="Yoshitomi &amp; Ruta" authorityYear="2010" box="[835,1062,1939,1964]" class="Insecta" family="Scirtidae" genus="Scirtes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malaccanus" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[835,1062,1939,1964]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Scirtes malaccanus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1069,1133,1938,1964]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, but with shorter penis.
</paragraph>
